20say%20that%20fuel%20shortages%20at%20the%20hospital%20and%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20unfolding%20near%20it%20are%20causing%20the%20deaths%20of%20patients%20%E2%80%93%20including%20newborns%20%E2%80%93%20and%20dead%20bodies%20to%20accumulate%20outside%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Advisor%E2%80%99s%20Appointment%20on%20Hydel%20Appraisal%20Committee%20Raises%20Conflict%20of%20Interest%20Concerns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12185403%2Fimage-1381.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20key%20advisor%20to%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Limited%20(AGEL)%20is%20now%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Expert%20Appraisal%20Committee%20(EAC)%2C%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20advises%20the%20government%20on%20environmental%20clearance%20of%20development%20projects.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2027%2C%20Janardan%20Choudhary%20was%20named%20as%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20non-institutional%20members%20of%20the%20reconstituted%20EAC%20by%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fadani-green-advisor-in-hydel-appraisal-committee-of-moef-9025521%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20EAC%20examined%20proposals%20related%20to%20hydroelectricity%20and%20river%20valley%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20at%20least%2010%20such%20EACs%20that%20decide%20environmental%20clearances%20on%20different%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAGEL%E2%80%99s%20hydro%20project%20proposals%20also%20came%20up%20for%20clearance%20at%20the%20EAC%2C%20which%20raises%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest%20issues%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20reconstituted%20EAC%20(hydel)%20was%20held%20on%20October%2017-18%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20cited%20records%20to%20say%20that%20Choudhary%20attended%20the%20meeting%20on%20October%2017.%20At%20the%20meeting%2C%20AGEL%E2%80%99s%201500%20megawatt%20Tarali%20Pumping%20Storage%20Project%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Satara%20came%20up%20for%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAGEL%20sought%20an%20amendment%20in%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20Terms%20of%20Reference%20(ToR)%20for%20a%20revision%20of%20the%20project%20layout%20after%20it%20realised%20that%20the%20proposed%20water%20conductor%20system%20passed%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20below%20an%20existing%20wind%20farm%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20construction%20underground%20or%20below%20the%20wind%20turbines%20foundations%20would%20be%20difficult%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20detailed%20deliberation%2C%20the%20EAC%20recommended%20in%20favour%20of%20AGEL%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Choudhury%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20take%20part%20in%20the%20discussion%20when%20the%20EAC%20considered%20the%20AEGL%20project.%20%E2%80%9CI%20abstained%20when%20the%20matter%20came%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20told%20that%20the%20minutes%20do%20not%20reflect%20this%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20amend%20the%20minutes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogendra%20Pal%20Singh%2C%20scientist%20(E)%20with%20the%20ministry%20and%20the%20member%20secretary%20of%20the%20EAC%20concerned%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Choudhary%20did%20not%20join%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20AEGL%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmere%20non-participation%20in%20the%20discussion%20by%20a%20member%20while%20his%20or%20her%20employer%E2%80%99s%20projects%20are%20considered%20is%20not%20sufficient.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20about%20the%20projects%20of%20his%20or%20her%20employer%E2%80%99s%20competitors%3F%20Or%20the%20scope%20for%20quid%20pro%20quo%20when%20such%20members%20return%20one%20another%20the%20favour%20even%20while%20abstaining%20from%20directly%20linked%20projects%3F%20More%20than%20establishing%20bias%2C%20the%20possibility%20of%20such%20bias%20is%20what%20matters%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20appointment%20conditions%20say%20that%20those%20who%20have%20provided%20consultancy%20services%20for%20a%20project%20proponent%20will%20recuse%20themselves%20from%20the%20process%20of%20appraisal%20of%20any%20project%20proposed%20by%20such%20proponents.%20We%20go%20by%20our%20rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20G.H.%20Chakrapani%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20IIT-Roorkee%20and%20chairperson%20of%20the%20EAC%20concerned%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Choudhary%20defended%20his%20position%20saying%20that%20the%20ministry%20is%20aware%20that%20he%20is%20an%20advisor%20with%20a%20private%20company.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20am%20nobody%E2%80%99s%20employee%20and%20I%20can%20advise%20others%20as%20well.%20My%20EAC%20appointment%20is%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20as%20a%20member%20I%20will%20give%20my%20opinion%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20EAC%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20LinkedIn%2C%20Choudhary%20worked%20as%20director%20(technical)%20at%20NHPC%20until%20March%202020.%20He%20has%20been%20an%20advisor%20(pumped%20storage%20plants%20and%20hydro)%20of%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Limited%20(AGEL)%20since%20April%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20reported%20that%20there%20are%20at%20least%20six%20AGEL%20projects%20before%20the%20EAC%2C%20which%20include%20the%20850%20MW%20Raiwada%20project%3B%201800%20MW%20Pedakota%20(both%20Andhra%20Pradesh)%3B%202100%20MW%20Patgaon%2C%202%2C450%20MW%20Koyna-Nivakane%2C%201500%20MW%20Malshej%20Ghat%20Bhorande%20and%201500%20MW%20Tarali%20(all%20Maharashtra).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C