o%20examination%20centres%20wearing%20the%20Hijab%20sparking%20off%20protests%20by%20right-wing%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20complaints%20of%20usage%20of%20Bluetooth%20devices%20by%20certain%20students%20the%20state%20government%20this%20time%20decided%20to%20enforce%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20government%20had%20on%20November%2011%20ordered%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20state%20CID%20into%20an%20incident%20where%20candidates%20at%20Kalaburagi%20and%20Yadgir%20examination%20centres%20allegedly%20used%20Bluetooth%20devices%20for%20writing%20the%20exams%20conducted%20by%20the%20KEA%20in%20October%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%20dress%20code%20restricts%20girls%20from%20wearing%20high%20heeled%20shoes%2C%20jeans%20and%20T-shirts%2C%20while%20men%20are%20permitted%20to%20wear%20half-sleeve%20shirts%20which%20are%20not%20tucked%20into%20their%20trousers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20upheld%20the%20Karnataka%20government's%20decision%20on%20banning%20the%20Hijab%20in%20classrooms%20that%20came%20under%20the%20state.%20The%20State%20government%20had%20at%20the%20time%20also%20extended%20this%20order%20to%20other%20Board%20exams%20like%20Class%20X%20and%20XII%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Common%20Entrance%20Test%20conducted%20by%20the%20KEA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699949280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fpclu1cvg_exam-generic_625x300_06_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-bans-head-cover-in-recruitment-exams-allows-mangalasutra-4572551%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20Examination%20Authority%20(KEA)%20restricted%20all%20forms%20of%20head%20cover%20in%20the%20exam%20hall%20during%20recruitment%20exams%20for%20various%20boards%20and%20corporations%20to%20avoid%20malpractice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-bans-head-cover-in-recruitment-exams-allows-mangalasutra-4572551%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-bans-head-cover-in-recruitment-exams-allows-mangalasutra-4572551%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-bans-head-cover-in-recruitment-exams-allows-mangalasutra-4572551%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WeWork%20Founder%20Living%20In%20A%20Lavish%20Miami%20Home%20As%20Company%20Collapses%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOffice%20space-sharing%20giant%20WeWork%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20in%20the%20United%20States%20last%20week%2C%20after%20the%20company%20struggled%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20effects%20of%20Covid-19%20and%20its%20failed%20initial%20public%20offering%20in%202019.%20Even%20as%20the%20company%20is%20financially%20struggling%2C%20the%20company's%20founder%2C%20Adam%20Neumann%2C%20has%20made%20headlines%20for%20his%20extravagant%20lifestyle.%20Notably%2C%20the%20American-Israeli%20entrepreneur%C2%A0was%20ousted%20after%20failing%20to%20take%20the%20company%20public%20through%20an%20initial%20public%20offering%20in%202019.%20But%20thanks%20to%20a%20hefty%20payout%2C%20Mr%20Neumann%20is%20now%20living%20in%20a%20'lavish'%20new%20home%20in%20Florida%20while%20building%20his%20new%20company%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F11%2F13%2Freal-estate%2Fwework-founder-adam-neumann-has-lavish-new-miami-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2044-year-old%20still%20has%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%241.7%20billion%20and%20owns%20millions%20in%20real%20estate.%20At%20present%2C%20he%20is%20living%20his%20best%20life%20in%20a%20luxurious%20mansion%C2%A0worth%20%2440%20million%2C%20with%20his%20wife%20Rebekah%2C%20and%20six%20children.%20He%20had%20purchased%20two%20Miami%20properties%20from%20local%20investor%20Joseph%20Imbesi%20for%20%2444%20million%20in%20an%20off-market%20deal%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Fmarkets%2Fwework-co-founder-adam-neumann-lavish-florida-mansion-bankrupt-company-reels-report%5C%22%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%2014%2C500-square-foot%20house%20was%20being%20built%20on%20the%20property%20at%20the%20time%20and%20it%20is%20now%20where%20Mr%20Neumann%20and%20his%20family%20live%20full-time.%20The%20sprawling%20mansion%20boasts%20breathtaking%20waterfront%20views%2C%20opulent%20amenities%2C%20and%20extravagant%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20said%2C%20''Adam%20skateboards%20all%20the%20time%2C%20all%20over%20town%2C%20taking%20business%20calls.%20Everybody%20runs%20into%20him%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20very%20friendly.%20He%20stops%20and%20kibitzes%20with%20people.''%20He%20is%20currently%20looking%20for%20investors%20for%20another%20startup%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20will%20reshape%20the%20world%20in%20the%20home%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Mr%20Newman%20is%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20Jared%20Kushner%20and%20Ivanka%20Trump%20and%20their%20children%2C%20who%20live%C2%A010%20minutes%20away%20from%20their%20home.%20The%20couple%20are%20also%20said%20to%20be%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20Jewish%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20his%20departure%20from%20WeWork%2C%20Mr%20Newman%20had%20spent%20%2490%20million%20to%20purchase%20luxury%20residential%20real%20estate%20in%20the%20Hamptons%2C%20New%20York%20City%2C%20and%20Westchester%20County%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20San%20Francisco%2C%C2%A0according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fwework-founder-adam-neumanns-trove-of-pricey-properties-11570730254%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Mr%20Neumann%20launched%20a%20new%20company%20called%20Flow%20that%20will%20operate%20in%20the%20residential%20real%20estate%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mr%20Neumann%20founded%20WeWork%C2%A0in%202010%2C%20and%20by%202019%2C%20it%20was%20worth%20%2447%20billion.%20When%20Mr%20Neumann%20left%20the%20company%2C%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20wealth%20was%20accumulated%20as%20it%20prepared%20for%20another%20public%20offering-%20time%20through%20a%20special%20purpose%20acquisition%20company%20(SPAC).%20In%202021%2C%20Mr%20Neumann%20reportedly%20received%20%24480%20million%20from%20SoftBank%20for%20half%20of%20his%20remaining%20WeWork%20stock%20as%20part%20of%20that%20SPAC%20process.%20Overall%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20Mr%20Neumann%20made%20over%20%24770%20million%20in%20cash%20from%20the%202021%20SPAC%20process%20alone%2C%20despite%20having%20been%20removed%20from%20a%20management%20position%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recently%20stated%20that%20WeWork's%20bankruptcy%20filing%20is%20%26quot%3Bdisappointing%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20has%20been%20hard%20for%20him%20to%20watch%20the%20company%20struggle.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20former%20WeWork%20staffer%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Post%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20morale%20at%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bhorrific%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20company%20culture%20and%20everybody%20is%20just%20watching%20the%20stock%20go%20down%2C%20down%2C%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699948860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Foh92jb7o_wework-founder_625x300_07_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbillionaire-wework-founder-adam-neumann-living-in-a-lavish-new-miami-home-as-company-goes-bankrupt-report-4572629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2044-year-old%20sti