r.com%2FFQx1dKiDlf%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Piyush%20Goyal%20(%40PiyushGoyal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPiyushGoyal%2Fstatus%2F1724262212146258204%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlso%20proud%20to%20see%20the%20growing%20importance%20of%20auto%20component%20suppliers%20from%20India%20in%20the%20Tesla%20EV%20supply%20chain.%20It%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20double%20its%20components%20imports%20from%20India.%20Missed%20Mr%20%40ElonMusk's%20magnetic%20presence%20and%20I%20wish%20him%20a%20speedy%20recovery%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20said%20on%20social%20networking%20platform%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20him%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20tweeted%2C%20''It%20was%20an%20honor%20to%20have%20you%20visit%20Tesla!%20My%20apologies%20for%20not%20being%20able%20to%20travel%20to%20California%20today%2C%20but%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20meeting%20at%20a%20future%20date.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20an%20honor%20to%20have%20you%20visit%20Tesla!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMy%20apologies%20for%20not%20being%20able%20to%20travel%20to%20California%20today%2C%20but%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20meeting%20at%20a%20future%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1724273310622487033%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%20cited%20by%20Reuters%2C%20Tesla%20is%20actively%20pursuing%20the%20establishment%20of%20an%20Indian%20factory%2C%20aiming%20to%20manufacture%20a%20%2424%2C000%20car%20within%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20assumes%20significance%20as%20there%20are%20reports%20that%20India%20is%20looking