0is%20left%20-%20and%20some%20had%20contracted%20gastritis%20and%20were%20suffering%20from%20diarrhoea%20and%20vomiting%2C%20which%20leaves%20them%20at%20risk%20of%20dehydration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20in%20a%20very%20bad%20situation...%20where%20you%20slowly%20kill%20them%20unless%20the%20situation%20improves...%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Ahmed%20El%20Mokhallalati%2C%20also%20involved%20in%20caring%20for%20the%20babies%2C%20told%20Reuters%20by%20telephone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20ensure%20the%20babies%20live%20-%20at%20least%20long%20enough%20to%20see%20the%20carnage%20and%20destruction%20wrought%20on%20Gaza%20by%20Israel%20and%20the%20Hamas%20-%20Dr%20Tabasha%20will%20need%20an%20uninterrupted%20supply%20of%20electricity%2C%20sterilisers%20for%20the%20milk%20and%20bottle%20teats%2C%20and%20support%20machines%20when%20any%20of%20them%20fall%20into%20respiratory%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20over%20650%20patients%20-%20waiting%20to%20be%20evacuated%20by%20the%20Red%20Cross%20-%20at%20the%20besieged%20Al%20Shifa%20Hospital%20that%20lacks%20essentials%20-%20diesel%2C%20food%2C%20water%2C%20medicines%20and%20medical%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-loses-contact-with-gaza-hospital-says-it-was-surrounded-by-tanks-4568183%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWHO%20Loses%20Contact%20With%20Gaza%20Hospital%20%26quot%3BSurrounded%20By%20Tanks%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20forces%20insist%20the%20hospital%20sits%20atop%20a%20network%20of%20tunnels%20that%20form%20part%20of%20the%20Hamas'%20underground%20headquarters%2C%20and%20that%20the%20group's%20operatives%20are%20using%20the%20patients%20as%20a%20shield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETel%20Aviv%20also%20insists%20it%20has%20evidence%20to%20show%20Hamas%20stored%20weapons%2C%20including%20grenades%2C%20suicide%20vests%20and%20other%20explosives%2C%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20another%20Gaza%20hospital.%20%26quot%3B...%20we%20also%20found%20signs%20that%20indicate%20that%20Hamas%20held%20hostages%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20a%20military%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas%2C%20and%20Gaza's%20health%20officials%2C%20have%20denied%20all%20such%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20said%20Monday%20that%20it%20had%20finally%20managed%20to%20re-establish%20contact%20with%20the%20Al%20Shifa%20Hospital%2C%20and%20warned%3B%20%26quot%3B...%20the%20hospital%20is%20not%20functioning%20as%20a%20hospital%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWHO%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40WHO%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20managed%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20health%20professionals%20at%20the%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGaza%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20situation%20is%20dire%20and%20perilous.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt's%20been%203%20days%20without%20electricity%2C%20without%20water%20and%20with%20very%20poor%20internet%20which%20has%20severely%20impacted%20our%20ability%20to%20provide%20essential%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%20(%40DrTedros)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrTedros%2Fstatus%2F1723795481401217509%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl%20Quds%2C%20a%20second%20major%20hospital%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20has%20been%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20world%20for%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Red%20Crescent%20said%20it%20was%20surrounded%20by%20heavy%20gunfire%2C%20and%20a%20convoy%20of%20Red%20Cross%20vehicles%20sent%20to%20evacuate%20patients%20