nd%20The%20Mystery%20of%20Solang%20Valley%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2066%2C%20Ratna%20Pathak%20Shah%20is%20living%20her%20best%2C%20with%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20roles%20that%20tap%20into%20her%20talent.%20She%20is%20not%20the%20one-dimensional%20mother%20of%20the%20yesteryears%2C%20and%20is%20raring%20to%20go%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20in%20film%2C%20in%20an%20OTT%20show%20or%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20she%20is%20back%20with%20an%20adaptation%20of%20Aleksei%20Arbuzov%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20stage%20with%20Naseeruddin%20Shah.%20The%20last%20time%20the%20couple%20was%20seen%20together%20on%20stage%2C%20with%20just%20each%20other%2C%20was%20in%20%3Cem%3EDear%20Liar%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Enearly%20two%20decades%20ago.%20Directed%20by%20Arghya%20Lahiri%2C%20the%20play%20is%20set%20in%20a%20medical%20sanitorium%20and%20is%20a%20rumination%20on%20old%20age%20and%20all%20that%20it%20brings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20doctor%20from%20Lucknow%2C%20she%20is%20a%20Parsi%20patient%20from%20Mumbai.%20Pathak%20Shah%20leans%20heavily%20on%20her%20Dadar%20Parsi%20Colony%20upbringing%2C%20where%20she%20was%20surrounded%20by%20Parsis%2C%20and%20the%20result%20is%20a%20quirky%20and%20endearing%20character.%20%3Cem%3EOld%20World%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20gentle%20and%20emotional.%20The%20characters%20bloom%2C%20and%20the%20Shahs%20shine%20once%20again.%20They%20reminisce%2C%20dance%2C%20sing%2C%20and%20speak%20of%20aging%20and%20love%20with%20rare%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20her%20cinematic%20pursuits%2C%20Pathak%20Shah%20never%20left%20the%20stage%2C%20returning%20at%20every%20chance%20she%20got%20to%20their%20company%20Motley%20Theatre.%20In%20an%20interview%2C%20she%20talks%20about%20%3Cem%3EDhak%20Dhak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20working%20with%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%20over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20hope%20she%20places%20on%20OTT%20content%2C%20and%20her%20undying%20love%20for%20live%20performance.%20Below%20are%20the%20edited%20excerpts%20of%20the%20interview%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Eve%20just%20had%20a%20big%20film%20release%20with%20%3Cem%3EDhak%20Dhak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20what%20was%20that%20like%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOh%20yes%2C%20%3Cem%3EDhak%20Dhak%3C%2Fem%3E%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20good%20film.%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20making%20%5Bof%20the%20film%5D.%20I%20was%20concerned%20about%20how%20the%20final%20product%20would%20be%2C%20but%20I%20was%20very%20pleased%20with%20the%20result.%20It%20is%20a%20moving%20and%20effective%20film%2C%20so%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Eve%20been%20quite%20vocal%20about%20older%20actresses%20not%20getting%20the%20roles%20they%20deserve%20in%20films.%20Do%20you%20think%20that%20is%20changing%3F%20Does%20this%20hold%20in%20theatre%2C%20too%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20do%20think%20there%20have%20been%20changes.%20Many%20more%20interesting%20parts%20are%20being%20written%20for%20actors%20of%20all%20ages.%20I%20think%20we%20are%20seeing%20quite%20a%20special%20moment%20in%20our%20journey%20of%20film%2C%20television%2C%20and%20OTT.%20Television%20has%20lagged%20but%20OTT%20has%20made%20a%20huge%20impact%20with%20different%20kinds%20of%20stories%20being%20told%2C%20different%20kinds%20of%20actors%20being%20cast%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20new%20kinds%20of%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20very%20hopeful.%20I%20am%20getting%20more%20interesting%20parts%20than%20my%20mother%20did%20at%20this%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20stage%20too%2C%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20have%20been%20writing%20material%20for%20themselves.%20We%20are%20not%20sitting%20down%20and%20waiting%20for%20others%20to%20write%20for%20us.%20Take%20Jyoti%20Dogra%20for%20example%2C%20or%20Divya%20Jagdale.%20They%20have%20been%20writing%20stories%20that%20mean%20things%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theatre%20is%20becoming%20a%20much%20more%20democratic%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaving%20worked%20with%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%20in%20both%20film%20and%20theatre%2C%20what%20do%20you%20enjoy%20most%20about%20working%20together%3F%20What%20have%20you%20learned%20from%20him%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20working%20with%20Naseer%20since%201975%2C%20and%20in%20quite%20a%20few%20productions%20he%20has%20directed.%20I%20can%20say%20honestly%20that%20I%20have%20learned%20most%20of%20what%20I%20know%20about%20acting%20from%20working%20with%20him%2C%20watching%20him%20work%2C%20and%20doing%20the%20workshops%20that%20he%20conducts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collaboration%20between%20us%20has%20been%20hugely%20beneficial%20for%20me.%20Naseer%20as%20a%20director%2C%20has%20been%20particularly%20wonderful%20for%20a%20play%20like%20%3Cem%3EIsmat%20Aapa%20Ke%20Naam%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20idea%20was%20his.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20we%20could%20pull%20it%20off%20beyond%20a%20few%20shows.%20After%20all%2C%20who%20would%20understand%20Urdu%20here%20in%20Mumbai%3F%20And%2022%20years%20later%2C%20we%20are%20still%20performing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20a%20lot%20during%20it.%20It%20clarified%20my%20ideas%20about%20acting%20and%20the%20craft%20%E2%80%93%20also%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20it.%20For%20me%2C%20%3Cem%3EIsmat%20Aapa%20Ke%20Naam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EDear%20Liar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20have%20both%20been%20colleges%20of%20acting.%20They%20helped%20me%20develop%20as%20a%20person%20and%20as%20an%20actor.%20And%20Naseer%E2%80%99s%20part%20in%20both%20of%20them%20has%20been%20extraordinary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20did%20not%20direct%20%3Cem%3EDear%20Liar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20have%20spent%20a%20long%20time%20with%20it.%20Now%2C%20what%20we%20are%20both%20doing%20is%20significantly%20more%20mature%2C%20more%20watchable%2C%20and%20more%20meaningful%20to%20us%20than%20when%20we%20first%20started%20doing%20the%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20an%20incredible%20journey%20and%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20Naseer%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20it%2C%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%20Sometimes%20showing%20the%20way%2C%20sometimes%20pulling%20me%20along%2C%20but%20always%20by%20my%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115502%2FOld-World-7.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115502%2FOld-World-7.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115502%2FOld-World-7-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115502%2FOld-World-7-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684639%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERatna%20Pathak%20Shah%2C%20on%20stage%20with%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%2C%20in%20an%20adaptation%20of%20Aleksei%20Arbuzov%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20working%20together%2C%20do%20the%20lines%20between%20rehearsals%20and%20home%20blur%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20preparation%20continues%20after%20rehearsal%20time%2C%20both%20individually%20and%20together.%20Both%20of%20us%20read%20our%20scripts%20quite%20often%20and%20for%20as%20long%20as%20we%20can.%20We%20read%20it%20together%20outside%20of%20rehearsal%20time%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20get%20to%20talk%20about%20it%20and%20share%20our%20ideas.%20That%20is%20very%20precious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20return%20to%20the%20stage%20with%20%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E.%20What%20is%20it%20that%20keeps%20you%20coming%20back%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20keep%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20stage%20because%20I%20love%20it%2C%20and%20it%20gives%20me%20the%20chance%20to%20play%20parts%20that%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%2C%20in%20film.%20It%20keeps%20me%20working%20regularly%20and%20engaging%20with%20a%20live%20audience%20every%20time.%20It%20helps%20me%20improve%20and%20change%20as%20the%20shows%20go%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20experience%20of%20working%20with%20a%20live%20audience%20is%20fabulous%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20give%20it%20up%20for%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14114715%2FOld-World-9.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14114715%2FOld-World-9.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14114715%2FOld-World-9-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14114715%2FOld-World-9-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684632%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERatna%20Pathak%20Shah%2C%20on%20stage%20with%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%2C%20in%20an%20adaptation%20of%20Aleksei%20Arbuzov%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20did%20you%20first%20read%20%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Aleksei%20Arbuzov%3F%20What%20was%20your%20reaction%20to%20it%20and%20how%20did%20you%20prepare%20for%20your%20character%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20seen%20the%20Kendals%20(Geoffrey%20and%20Laura)%20do%20%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E%20many%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20I%20had%20read%20the%20script%20before.%20When%20Naseer%20decided%20to%20do%20it%2C%20I%20reread%20the%20script%20and%20found%20that%20it%20had%20great%20possibilities.%20It%20spoke%20to%20me%20at%20this%20stage%20in%20my%20life%20very%20clearly.%20I%20found%20many%20resonances%20with%20the%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArghya%20Lahiri%2C%20the%20director%2C%20and%20I%20started%20reading%20the%20play%20together%20in%20April.%20We%20started%20working%20on%20it%20in%20August%2C%20so%20we%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20with%20the%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20I%20approached%20this%20script%20and%20the%20character%20is%20the%20same%20as%20every%20other%20time%2C%20which%20is%20by%20reading%20the%20script%20as%20many%20times%20as%20I%20can%2C%20and%20imagining%20what%20I%20would%20be%20if%20I%20were%20in%20this%20situation%20and%20I%20was%20this%20person.%20It%20helps%20me%20create%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20character%20in%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20process%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20reading%2C%20practice%2C%20and%20a%20large%20dollop%20of%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20difficult%20has%20it%20been%20to%20work%20together%20in%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20piece%20that%20is%20vulnerable%20and%20addresses%20the%20complexities%20of%20old%20age%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20difficult%20at%20all%20and%20it%20has%20been%20a%20pleasure%20all%20over%20again.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us%20after%20a%20long%20time%2C%20since%20%3Cem%3EDear%20Liar.%3C%2Fem%3E%20So%2C%20there%20is%20a%20special%20feeling%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20piece%2C%20%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20something%20we%20have%20thought%20about%20a%20lot%20and%20experienced%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20have%20been%20spoken%20about%20in%20the%20play.%20It%20resonates%20with%20me%20as%20I%20grow%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20positive%20take%20on%20this%20issue.%20There%20is%20no%20moaning%20and%20groaning.%20Most%20Indian%20plays%20on%20old%20age%20tend%20to%20be%20extremely%20sentimental%20and%20make%20old%20people%20into%20poor%20old%20things.%20This%20play%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20It%20shows%20them%20as%20vibrant%20human%20beings%20with%20different%20approaches%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20while%20since%20you%20directed%20a%20play.%20What%20keeps%20you%20away%20from%20directing%20for%20the%20stage%3F%20What%20about%20film%2C%20is%20that%20something%20you%20would%20want%20to%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20it%20has%20been%20quite%20a%20while.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20found%20anything%20I%20would%20like%20to%20direct.%20The%20last%20two%20experiences%20I%20had%20weren%E2%80%99t%20satisfactory%20and%20I%20need%20to%20brush%20up%20my%20skills%20before%20I%20try%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20I%20will%20try%20directing%20a%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20comments%20on%20the%20current%20state%20of%20contemporary%20theatre%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20India%3F%20What%20are%20some%20of%20the%20significant%20changes%20you%20see%20today%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheatre%20is%20going%20through%20a%20rather%20challenging%20phase.%20It%20may%20not%20appear%20so%20when%20you%20are%20at%20Prithvi%20Theatre.%20Elsewhere%2C%20it%20is%20a%20problem%2C%20particularly%20with%20the%20bigger%20theatre%20groups.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20as%20much%20of%20a%20commercially%20viable%20proposition%20as%20it%20used%20to%20be.%20Television%20and%20OTT%20have%20eaten%20into%20the%20audiences.%20Also%2C%20the%20distances%20and%20commute%20have%20made%20it%20more%20difficult.%20Not%20to%20mention%20the%20pandemic%20and%20the%20lockdown%20that%20pulled%20the%20rug%20from%20under%20our%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20has%20spawned%20all%20sorts%20of%20theatrical%20activity%20and%20people%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20imagine%20performance%20in%20different%20ways%20and%20not%20just%20in%20a%20physical%20theatre.%20They%20are%20productions%20that%20could%20be%20done%20in%20someone%E2%80%99s%20drawing%20room%2C%20in%20a%20small%20theatre%20space%2C%20in%20a%20black%20box%2C%20on%20the%20street%2C%20or%20in%20a%20garden.%20This%20flexibility%20of%20ideas%20and%20these%20imaginative%20theatre%20techniques%20have%20been%20a%20source%20of%20hope%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theatre%20will%20find%20different%20forms%20now%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20fulfil%20its%20real%20purpose%2C%20which%20is%20to%20have%20contact%20with%20each%20member%20of%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20any%20recent%20theatre%20productions%20that%20you%20have%20watched%20and%20enjoyed%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20enjoyed%20%3Cem%3ESangeet%20Bari%3C%2Fem%3E%20(written%20by%20Bhushan%20Korgaonkar%20and%20directed%20by%20Savitri%20Medhatul)%20very%20much.%20Apart%20from%20being%20informative%2C%20it%20was%20entertaining%20and%20beautiful%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20equally%20loved%20%3Cem%3EJo%20Dooba%20So%20Paar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(written%20by%20Ajitesh%20Gupta%2C%20and%20directed%20by%20Ajitesh%20Gupta%20and%20Mohit%20Agarwal)%2C%20based%20on%20the%20life%20of%20Amir%20Khusrau.%20The%20energy%20of%20the%20performers%2C%20how%20the%20story%20was%20told%2C%20and%20the%20absolute%20magic%20of%20the%20singing.%20I%20enjoyed%20everything%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20another%20one%2C%20quite%20different%20in%20mood%2C%20was%20Akarsh%20Khurana%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20F%20Word%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20found%20it%20imaginatively%20staged%2C%20and%20talking%20about%20something%20that%20is%20a%20part%20of%20our%20lives%20and%20will%20be%20more%20so%2C%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20writer%20%3Cspan%3Eis%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3EMumbai-based%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699944874000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14120232%2FOld-World-1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fratna-pathak-shah-on-life-work-film-and-theatre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%2C%20Pathak%20Shah%20speaks%20about%20her%20last%20film%20'Dhak%20Dhak'%2C%20the%20evolving%20OTT%20space%2C%20and%20her%20return%20to%20the%20stage%20with%20a%20play%20that%20speaks%20of%20love%2C%20loss%2C%20and%20ageing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fratna-pathak-shah-on-life-work-film-and-theatre%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindustan%20Unilever%20to%20help%20kirana%20stores%20compete%20with%20big%20cos%20via%20ONDC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699944753000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-12%2F18%2Ffull%2F1576615094-2695.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhindustan-unilever-to-help-kirana-stores-compete-with-big-cos-via-ondc-123111400302_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hindustan%20Unilever%20(HUL)%20became%20the%20first%20fast-moving%20consumer%20goods%20(FMCG)%20company%20to%20join%20ONDC%20last%20year%20through%20UShop%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhindustan-unilever-to-help-kirana-stores-compete-with-big-cos-via-ondc-123111400302_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhindustan-unilever-to-help-kirana-stores-compete-with-big-cos-via-ondc-123111400302_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww