Jinping%20in%20San%20Francisco%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20he%20seeks%20to%20court%20American%20companies%20and%20counter%20his%20country's%20recent%20struggles%20to%20entice%20foreign%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dinner%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%20forum%20will%20follow%20a%20day%20of%20talks%20between%20Xi%20and%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20aimed%20at%20stabilizing%20fraught%20ties%20between%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20American%20businesses%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20chance%20to%20hear%20directly%20from%20China's%20leader%20as%20they%20search%20for%20ways%20to%20navigate%20China's%20economic%20slowdown%2C%20a%20US%20push%20to%20%26quot%3Bde-risk%26quot%3B%20some%20American%20supply%20chains%20away%20from%20China%2C%20and%20uncertainty%20caused%20by%20expanding%20Chinese%20security%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20dinner%20is%20to%20foster%20better%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20source%20close%20to%20the%20organizers%20told%20Reuters%2C%20declining%20to%20say%20who%20would%20speak%20while%20confirming%20representatives%20from%20both%20the%20Chinese%20and%20U.S.%20governments%20would%20share%20the%20podium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20event%2C%20yet%20to%20be%20formally%20announced%20by%20hosts%20US-China%20Business%20Council%20(USCBC)%20and%20the%20National%20Committee%20on%20US-China%20Relations%20(NCUSCR)%2C%20also%20presents%20uneasy%20optics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20event%20notifications%20seen%20by%20Reuters%2C%20some%20US%20firms%20will%20pay%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20hear%20a%20%26quot%3BChinese%20state%20leader%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20government%20that%20Washington%20has%20accused%20of%20genocide%20against%20Muslim%20Uyghurs.%20China%20has%20vigorously%20denied%20the%20accusations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20USCBC%20and%20NCUSCR%20both%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20planned%20dinner.%20China's%20embassy%20in%20Washington%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%2C%20who%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20deliver%20a%20speech%2C%20will%20be%20eager%20to%20convince%20US%20industry%20that%20China%20is%20still%20open%20for%20business%20after%20recording%20its%20first%20quarterly%20deficit%20in%20foreign%20direct%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20China%20this%20year%20cast%20off%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20controls%20that%20effectively%20shut%20its%20borders%2C%20it%20has%20grown%20more%20suspicious%20of%20engagement%20with%20Western%20companies%2C%20in%20line%20with%20Xi's%20emphasis%20on%20national%20security.%20Xi%20has%20overseen%20a%20crackdown%20on%20US%20consultancy%20and%20due-diligence%20firms%2C%20a%20further%20blow%20to%20investor%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Filet%20Mignon'%20And%20Human%20Rights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20business%20and%20trade%20has%20been%20at%20the%20center%20of%20US-China%20relations%2C%20helping%20to%20fuel%20China's%20explosive%20economic%20resurgence%20and%20offering%20what%20Beijing%20has%20often%20described%20as%20the%20ballast%20in%20otherwise%20contentious%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20concerns%20about%20a%20new%20style%20cold%20war%20between%20the%20rival%20economic%20and%20geopolitical%20superpowers%20has%20increasingly%20placed%20companies%20in%20the%20cross%20hairs%20of%20both%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%20is%20on%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%20more%20than%20six%20years%20and%20the%20pricey%20dinner%2C%20up%20to%20%2440%2C000%20for%20a%20table%20of%20eight%2C%20according%20to%20one%20notice%20for%20the%20event%2C%20is%20routine%20by%20standards%20for%20past%20Chinese%20presidential%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20was%20not%20able%20to%20obtain%20a%20list%20of%20attendees%2C%20but%20executives%20of%20some%20companies%20who%20spoke%20privately%20to%20Reuters%20said%20they%20would%20steer%20clear%20given%20questions%20about%20the%20utility%20for%20their%20operations%20in%20China%20and%20US%20political%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeff%20Moon%2C%20a%20former%20US%20trade%20official%20turned%20business%20adviser%2C%20said%20China's%20goal%20would%20be%20to%20soften%20Xi's%20image%20and%20attract%20investment%2C%20but%20that%20the%20dinner%20was%20unlikely%20to%20%26quot%3Bmove%20any%20needles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20lawmakers%20have%20castigated%20some%20American%20businesses%20for%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20allegations%20of%20forced%20labor%20in%20China%20and%20some%20have%20been%20scathing%20in%20their%20criticism%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20does%20that%20dinner%20conversation%20go%3F%20'Wow%2C%20this%20filet%20mignon%20is%20a%20little%20dry.%20How's%20your%20extrajudicial%20internment%20of%20over%20a%20million%20Uyghur%20Muslims%20going%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Mike%20Gallagher%2C%20the%20Republican%20chair%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Representative's%20select%20committee%20on%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20human%20rights%20concerns%2C%20Biden%20has%20made%20a%20diplomatic%20push%20to%20improve%20relations%2C%20which%20slid%20to%20what%20many%20analysts%20viewed%20as%20an%20all-time%20low%20after%20the%20US%20shot%20down%20an%20alleged%20Chinese%20spy%20balloon%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20says%20communication%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20is%20essential%20to%20prevent%20competition%20veering%20into%20conflict%2C%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20global%20economy%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Janet%20Yellen%20reiterated%20ahead%20of%20the%20APEC%20summit%20that%20while%20the%20US%20sought%20to%20reduce%20its%20dependence%20on%20China%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20it%20did%20not%20seek%20broad%20economic%20decoupling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dinner%20is%20Xi's%20%26quot%3Breassurance%20tour%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20business%20leaders%20would%20look%20to%20him%20to%20set%20expectations%20for%20how%20foreign%20companies%20would%20be%20treated%20in%20China%2C%20said%20Nirav%20Patel%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20consultancy%20The%20Asia%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20come%20to%20accept%20that%20there's%20no%20substitute%20for%20hearing%20and%20seeing%20and%20observing%20what%20Xi%20Jinping%20is%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Patel.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20there%20are%20some%20that%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20they%20are%20committed%20to%20China%20and%20their%20presence%20in%20these%20meetings%20demonstrates%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699943700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F865t1f7_xi-jinping-reuters_625x300_18_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-firms-to-pay-tens-of-thousands-of-dollars-for-dinner-with-xi-report-4572482%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Top%20business%20leaders%20in%20the%20United%20States%20are%20expected%20to%20dine%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20in%20San%20Francisco%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20he%20seeks%20to%20court%20American%20companies%20and%20counter%20his%20country's%20recent%20struggles%20to%20entice%20foreign%20investment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-firms-to-pay-tens-of-thousands-of-dollars-for-dinner-with-xi-report-4572482%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-firms-to-pay-tens-of-thousands-of-dollars-for-dinner-with-xi-report-4572482%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-firms-to-pay-tens-of-thousand