0efforts%20continue%20today%2C%20November%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20portion%20of%20an%20under-construction%20tunnel%20between%20Silkyara%20and%20Dandalgaon%20on%20the%20Brahmakhal-Yamunotri%20national%20highway%20gave%20away%20during%20a%20landslide%2C%20trapping%20the%20workers.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Uttarkashi%20district.%20The%20collapsed%20stretch%2C%20it%20has%20been%20reported%2C%20is%20around%20200%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67411822%3Fat_link_id%3D6E764E72-82AB-11EE-A3D8-ECE2A9F30DC0%26at_medium%3Dsocial%26at_campaign%3DSocial_Flow%26at_ptr_name%3Dtwitter%26at_bbc_team%3Deditorial%26at_link_type%3Dweb_link%26at_campaign_type%3Downed%26at_link_origin%3DBBCWorld%26at_format%3Dlink%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20established%20contact%20with%20the%20trapped%20men%20on%20Sunday%20night%20using%20walkie-talkies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-uttarkashi-tunnel-collapse-at-uttarakhand-tunnel-rescue-op-enters-day-3-new-machine-drill-in-action-4572039%5C%22%3Ereported%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20around%2021%20metres%20have%20been%20removed%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20create%20a%2040-metre%20escape%20passage.%20Pipes%C2%A0%20will%20be%20pushed%20through%20this%20passage%20so%20that%20the%20workers%20can%20squeeze%20through%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20a%20buffer%20of%20around%20400%20metres%20to%20walk%20and%20breathe%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdehradun-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-auger-drilling-machines-at-site-to-evacuate-workers-101699933841710.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20National%20Highways%20%26amp%3B%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20has%20said%20that%20auger%20drilling%20machines%20will%20be%20employed%20to%20drill%20this%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tunnel%20under%20construction%20where%20the%20workers%20have%20been%20trapped%20since%20Sunday%20is%20part%20of%20the%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20and%20controversial%20Char%20Dham%20road%20project%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways.%20The%20Project%20aims%20to%20widen%20around%20900%20km%20of%20existing%20national%20highways%20that%20connect%20several%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Uttarakhand%20including%20Badrinath%20and%20Kedarnath%2C%20up%20to%20the%20Indo-Tibet%20border.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20has%20cited%20both%20national%20security%20concerns%20and%20improving%20tourist%20footfall%20and%20amenities%20as%20reasons%20for%20converting%20the%20existing%20highways%20into%20double-laned%2C%2012-14%20meter-wide%20roads%20with%20a%20paved%20shoulder%20configuration%20for%20674%20km%20till%20the%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExperts%2C%20however%2C%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsupreme-court-char-dham-highway-national-security-wider-landslide-prone-roads-uttarakhand%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20several%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20Project.%20These%20pertain%20to%20the%20geological%20stability%20of%20the%20mountain%20range%2C%20the%20impacts%20of%20the%20expansion%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20fragile%20mountain%20ecology%20and%20the%20environment%20(due%20to%20the%20cutting%20of%20hills%20and%20deforestation)%2C%20and%20the%20subsequent%20impacts%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20landslides%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20construction%20for%20the%20wider%20highway%20will%20have%20on%20local%20communities.%20In%20early%20January%20this%20year%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20town%20of%20Joshimath%20%E2%80%93%20a%20hill%20town%20in%20the%20state%20near%20which%20one%20segment%20of%20the%20Char%20Dham%20road%20project%20passes%20%E2%80%93%20faced%20land%20subsidence%2C%20or%20the%20sinking%20of%20land%20which%20caused%20cracks%20to%20develop%20on%20houses%20and%20other%20buildings%20in%20the%20town.%20Experts%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fjoshimath-himalayas-explainer-warnings-reports-construction-ntpc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20ground%20drilling%20and%20the%20use%20of%20explosives%20for%20the%20Char%20Dham%20highway%20project%20were%20also%20among%20the%20factors%20that%20destabilized%20the%20town.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20project%20proponents%20broke%20up%20the%20~900%20km%20project%20into%20more%20than%2050%20separate%20ones%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fit-doesnt-make-sense-for-char-dham-project-case-to-be-heard-by-a-new-bench%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecircumnavigate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20need%20for%20an%20Environmental%20Impact%20Assessment%20of%20the%20project.%20Though%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20was%20formed%20to%20advise%20the%20government%20on%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20environmental%20impacts%2C%20its%20recommendations%20were%20not%20taken%20into%20consideration%20and%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20committee%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fchairman-of-sc-formed-char-dham-panel-resigns-101644516458571.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresigned%20in%20protest%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20February%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699943022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115024%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.50.16%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Futtara