0New%20Zealand%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20it%20is%20needless%20to%20say%20that%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20will%20be%20a%20top%20target.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERachin%20Ravindra%20is%20an%20Indian%20origin%20player.%20His%20grandparents%20live%20in%20Bengaluru.%20He%20even%20visited%20them%20during%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%20There%20is%20a%20popular%20story%20that%20the%20name%20'Rachin'%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20names%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Rachin's%20father%20has%20now%20clarified%20that%20the%20given%20name%20was%20not%20intentional.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Rachin%20was%20born%2C%20my%20wife%20suggested%20the%20name%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20discussing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ravi%20Krishnamurthy%2C%20Ravindra's%20father%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fsport%2Frachin-rachin-bangalore-boy-is-new-zealands-breakout-star-and-he-is-just-getting-started%2F1841557%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20name%20sounded%20good%2C%20was%20easy%20to%20spell%2C%20and%20short%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20with%20it.%20It%20was%20only%20some%20years%20later%20that%20we%20realised%20the%20name%20was%20a%20mix%20of%20Rahul%20and%20Sachin's%20names.%20He%20wasn't%20named%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20make%20our%20child%20a%20cricketer%20or%20anything%20of%20the%20sort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoungster%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20recently%20talked%20about%20his%20journey%20of%20breaking%20into%20the%20New%20Zealand%20team%20and%20living%20his%20childhood%20dream%20of%20the%20crowd%20chanting%20his%20name%20while%20he%20was%20performing%20on%20the%20field%20of%20cricket.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20the%20time%20frame%20of%20the%20past%20year%20to%20six%20months%20Rachin%20was%20not%20even%20close%20to%20breaking%20New%20Zealand's%20playing%20XI%2C%20but%20now%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20talent%20to%20watch%20out%20for%20by%20scoring%20three%20tons%20in%20the%20ongoing%20World%20Cup%20and%20featuring%20in%20the%20Top-5%20run%20scorers%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%2042%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20took%20the%20Kiwis%20a%20step%20closer%20to%20qualifying%20for%20the%20semi-finals.%20While%20talking%20to%20Star%20Sports%20after%20the%20game%2C%20the%2023-year-old%20youngster%20talked%20about%20his%20journey%20which%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20fairy%20tale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pretty%20surreal%20feeling.%20Grateful%20for%20the%20support%2C%20especially%20playing%20in%20Bangalore.%20Crowd%20chanting%20my%20name%20is%20something%20I%20will%20never%20take%20for%20granted.%20Dreamt%20of%20it%20as%20a%20child.%20Very%20happy%20to%20be%20here%2C%20lucky%20enough%20it%20worked%20out.%20Six%20to%2012%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20not%20even%20in%20the%20frame.%20Good%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done%20and%20get%20into%20the%20playoffs.%20Lucky%20enough%20to%20have%20come%20here%20in%20my%20teenage%20years%20on%20club%20tours.%20That%20has%20helped%20me%20a%20lot.%20Nice%20wickets%20to%20bat%20on.%20If%20you%20play%20positive%20cricket%2C%20you%20get%20rewarded.%20The%20guys%20have%20adapted%20well.%20You%20talk%20to%20Kane%2C%20Devon%2C%20who%20are%20legends%2C%26quot%3B%20Rachin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ewith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699942080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fm8jg03ho_rachin-ravindra_625x300_28_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fno-rachin-ravindra-was-not-named-after-rahul-dravid-and-sachin-tendulkar-father-says-didnt-spend-4572408%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20565%20runs%20in%20nine%20innings%2C%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20is%20the%20third-highest%20scorer%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fno-rachin-ravindra-was-not-named-after-rahul-dravid-and-sachin-tendulkar-father-says-didnt-spend-4572408%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fno-rachin-ravindra-was-not-named-after-rahul-dravid-and-sachin-tendulkar-father-says-didnt-spend-4572408%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fno-rachin-ravindra-was-not-named-after-rahul-dravid-and-sachin-tendulkar-father-says-didnt-spend-4572408%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Govt%20Notifies%20Norms%20Giving%20Itself%20Absolute%20Control%20on%20IIM%20Boards%2C%20Appointment%20of%20Directors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14094307%2FIIMB_entrance.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20move%20that%20significantly%20undermines%20the%20autonomy%20of%20the%20various%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Management%20(IIMs)%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20will%20now%20control%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20board%20of%20governors%20and%20directors%20in%20the%20institutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20new%20norms%20notified%20by%20the%20government%20on%20November%2010%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fnov%2F14%2Fcentre-takes-control-of-iims-president-to-pick-their-directors-2632661.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20President%20of%20India%20will%20be%20the%20Visitor%20of%20each%20IIM%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20through%20whom%20the%20government%20will%20have%20the%20final%20say%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20board%20and%20the%20director%20of%20the%20institutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Frajya-sabha-passes-bill-to-make-president-visitor-at-iims-raises-concerns-over-autonomy-and-funding-101691508125232.html%5C%22%3EIndian%20Institutes%20of%20Management%20(IIM)%20(Amendment)%20Bill%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20meant%20to%20amend%20the%202017%20IIM%20Act%20%E2%80%93%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20August%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20newly%20notified%20norms%2C%20the%20government%20has%20also%20changed%20the%20eligibility%20criteria%20for%20IIM%20directors%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fnov%2F14%2Fcentre-takes-control-of-iims-president-to-pick-their-directors-2632661.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20new%20norms%20make%20a%20first%20class%20degree%20in%20in%20both%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20and%20Master%E2%80%99s%20mandatory%20along%20with%20a%20PhD%20or%20an%20equivalent%20qualification%20from%20a%20reputed%20institute%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20has%20come%20in%20effect%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20reappointment%20of%20Dheeraj%20Sharma%20as%20IIM-Rohtak%E2%80%99s%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharma%20had%20misrepresented%20his%20academic%20credentials%20during%20his%20initial%20appointment%2C%20which%20occurred%20before%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%20IIM%20Act.%20He%20had%20a%20second%20class%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20first%20class%2C%20which%20was%20a%20mandatory%20eligibility%20requirement%20for%20the%20job%20as%20per%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20advertisement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20education%20ministry%20found%20out%20about%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20deceptive%20actions%2C%20it%20was%20unable%20to%20prevent%20his%20re-appointment%20for%20a%20second%20term%20last%20year.%20This%20was%20because%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20re-appointment%2C%20the%20IIM%20Rohtak%20Board%20had%20the%20absolute%20power%20under%20the%20IIM%20Act%20to%20choose%20the%20director%20and%20it%20had%20not%20stipulated%20a%20first-class%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20and%20Master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20as%20a%20mandatory%20criterion%2C%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fpublic-interest-to-orders-ignored-govt-gets-power-to-dissolve-iim-boards-9022259%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20the%20president%20will%20now%20have%20the%20powers%20to%20appoint%20and%20remove%20directors%20and%20dissolve%20the%20boards%2C%20if%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20revised%20process%2C%20the%20search%20and%20selection%20committee%20will%20submit%20a%20roster%20of%20three%20candidates%20under%20consideration%20for%20the%20directorial%20position%20to%20the%20Visitor.%20If%20the%20Visitor%20is%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20proposed%20names%2C%20they%20can%20seek%20fresh%20recommendations%20from%20the%20same%20committee%20or%20constitute%20a%20fresh%20search-cum-selection%20committee%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%20the%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIM%E2%80%99s%20had%20resisted%20the%20provision%20of%20a%20Visitor%20in%202015%20when%20the%20draft%20of%20the%20IIM%20Act%20was%20released.%20They%20had%20maintained%20that%20the%20move%20would%20undermine%20their%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699941968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14094307%2FIIMB_entrance.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Funion-govt-notifies-norms-giving-itself-absolute-control-on-iim-boards-appointment-of-directors%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20President%20of%20India%20will%20now%20be%20the%20Visitor%20of%20each%20IIM%2C%20through%20whom%20the%20government%20will%20have%20the%20final%20say%20in%20appointment%20of%20the%20boards'%20chairperson%20and%20director.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Funion-govt-notifies-norms-giving-itself-absolute-control-on-iim-boards-appointment-of-directors%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20Telangana%20Elections%2C%20Gig%20Workers'%20Union%20Demands%20a%20Rajasthan-Like%20Welfare%20Law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F12090306%2F22.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Platform%20Based%20Gig%20Workers%20(Registration%20and%20Welfare%20Act)%20has%20become%20a%20model%20for%20gig%20workers%20to%20raise%20their%20issues%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20Telangana%20Gig%20and%20Platform%20Workers%20Union%20(TGPWU)%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20Indian%20Federation%20Of%20App-Based%20Transport%20Workers(I-FAT)%2C%20has%20been%20demanding%20to%20start%20the%20process%20for%20establishing%20a%20welfare%20law%20in%20Telangana.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20union%20has%20been%20engaging%20with%20the%20government%2C%20protesting%20and%20promoting%20gig%20workers%E2%80%99%20rights%20across%20the%20state%2C%20and%20this%20election%20could%20determine%20their%20labour%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rise%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Furban-company-sues-workers-for-protesting-against-unfair-labour-practices-protest-called-off%5C%22%3Eplatform%20capitalism%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20away%20labour%20rights%20of%20workers%20by%20forcing%20new%20terminologies%20for%20workers%20as%20%E2%80%98partners%E2%80%99.%20This%20issue%20has%20led%20to%20a%20host%20of%20issues%20with%20platform%20workers%20unable%20to%20access%20basic%20labour%20rights%20from%20the%20platforms.%20The%20nature%20of%20work%20has%20been%20changed%20to%20force%20the%20workers%20to%20act%20according%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20market%20with%20black%20box%20algorithms.%20The%20workers%20themselves%20are%20aware%20of%20this%20change%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20work%2C%20with%20how%20the%20platform%20has%20been%20seeking%20more%20rent%20from%20them%2C%20and%20the%20demands%20of%20fair%20pay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telangana%20platform%20workers%E2%80%99%20movement%20has%20been%20central%20to%20the%20platform%20workers%E2%80%99%20rights%20in%20India%2C%20with%20its%20union%20leader%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frestofworld.org%2F2023%2Findia-powerful-uber-driver%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EShaik%20Salauddin%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20who%20has%20been%20on%20the%20forefront%20of%20challenging%20the%20platform%20companies.%20Shaik%E2%80%99s%20interaction%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20in%202022%20resulted%20in%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20working%20towards%20the%20Rajasthan%20law.%20The%20Congress%20in%20Karnataka%20also%20introduced%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fkarnataka-govt-rolls-out-health-accident-insurance-to-gig-economy-workers-2680823%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Escheme%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20towards%20the%20insurance%20of%20platform%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20282px)%2085vw%2C%20282px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14103400%2Fimage-1496.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22282%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14103400%2Fimage-1496.png%20282w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14103400%2Fimage-1496-134x300.png%20134w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684609%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20a%20trip%20where%20a%20driver%20has%20been%20just%20paid%20Rs%20337.15%20for%20a%2030%20kilometre%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20actions%20are%20now%20increasing%20pressure%20on%20political%20parties%20in%20Telangana%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20India%20to%20take%20platform%20workers%E2%80%99%20problems%20seriously.%20The%20workers%20themselves%20have%20been%20protesting%20innovatively%20across%20Telangana%2C%20and%20these%20practices%20have%20been%20adopted%20across%20India.%20Protest%20forms%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frestofworld.org%2F2022%2Fuber-ola-drivers-protest%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eswitching%20off%20AC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20due%20to%20low%20fares%20are%20continuously%20being%20used%20by%20cab%20drivers%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20protest.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpecifically%2C%20fares%20to%20the%20Hyderabad%20airport%20and%20from%20the%20airport%20are%20quite%20low%20for%20the%20drivers%3B%20the%20fare%20only%20covers%20the%20fuel%20charges%2C%20leading%20to%20these%20protests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20constant%20demand%20from%20the%20union%20has%20been%20to%20make%20the%20platform%20companies%20give%20back%20the%20data%20of%20the%20trips%20back%20to%20the%20platform%20workers.%20In%20a%20recent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defindia.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FData-Justic-Book_For-website.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublication%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Shaik%20Saluddin%20argued%20that%20as%20partners%20of%20these%20platforms%2C%20workers%20need%20to%20be%20supplied%20with%20information%20as%20the%20company%20would%20do%20during%20an%20initial%20public%20offering.%20The%20union%20has%20questioned%20the%20information%20asymmetry%20being%20created%20by%20the%20companies.%20It%20wants%20the%20drivers%20to%20have%20their%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20platform%20workers%20are%20also%20aware%20of%20how%20the%20algorithms%20are%20taking%20control%20of%20their%20lives%20and%20have%20been%20demanding%20changes%20on%20who%20gets%20a%20trip%20allocated.%20Platforms%20could%20be%20allocating%20more%20work%20to%20workers%20who%20have%20taken%20a%20loan%20or%20have%20enrolled%20into%20different%20programmes%20by%20platform%20companies.%20This%20understanding%20of%20the%20rating%20algorithms%20is%20what%20makes%20the%20platform%20workers%20to%20demand%205%20star%20ratings%20from%20the%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20the%20issue%20of%20lower%20fare%20or%20being%20discriminated%20against%20by%20the%20algorithms%2C%20platform%20workers%20are%20questioning%20their%20digital%20exile%20from%20the%20platforms.%20Their%20platform%20worker%20IDs%20are%20blocked%20for%20protesting%2C%20or%20receiving%20complaints%20from%20customers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telangana%20Gig%20and%20Platform%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Union%20deals%20with%20an%20average%20of%2025-30%20workers%20whose%20IDs%20are%20blocked%20by%20the%20platforms.%20Most%20of%20the%20workers%20are%20unaware%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20blocks%2C%20and%20getting%20IDs%20unblocked%20is%20a%20tedious%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20alienation%20of%20workers%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20platforms%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20work%20in%20conditions%20that%20are%20not%20always%20in%20their%20favour.%20The%20union%20wants%20a%20grievance%20redressal%20platform%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20of%20drivers.%20In%20addition%2C%20they%20have%20been%20demanding%20for%20customer%20KYC%20(know%20your%20customer)%2C%20because%20customers%20themselves%20could%20behave%20unruly.%20How%20society%20has%20been%20treating%20platform%20workers%20without%20the%20dignity%20they%20deserve%20is%20often%20reflected%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20disagreements%20between%20the%20worker%20and%20the%20unruly%20demands%20of%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20platform%20workers%20face%20exploitation%20in%20terms%20of%20fair%20pay%2C%20they%20also%20lack%20support%20from%20the%20welfare%20institutions%20in%20Telangana.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20Telangana%20cancelled%20ration%20cards%20of%20people%20owning%20a%20car.%20It%20also%20cancelled%20access%20to%20ration%20for%20all%20car-owning%20drivers%20too.%20Access%20to%20accident%20insurance%2C%20state%20welfare%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20work%20conditions%20are%20a%20constant%20issue%20of%20concern%20for%20platform%20workers%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202023%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffair.work%2Fen%2Ffw%2Fpublications%2Ffairwork-india-ratings-2023-labour-standards-in-the-platform-economy%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Fairwork%20Project%20on%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20platform%20workers%20presents%20the%20current%20status%20of%20workers%20across%20India.%20It%20scores%20platform%20companies%20across%20different%20areas%20like%20pay%2C%20conditions%20of%20work%2C%20management%2C%20contracts%20and%20representation.%20The%20report%20shows%20how%20alienation%20of%20workers%20continues%20to%20occur%20in%20India%20amplified%20with%20algorithms%2C%20consumer%20rating%20and%20lack%20of%20government%20regulation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlatform%20companies%20push%20back%20against%20government%20regulation%20while%20employing%20union-busting%20methods%20such%20as%20blocking%20IDs%20and%20giving%20incentives%20to%20workers%20on%20the%20day%20of%20a%20strike%20announcement.%20While%20the%20unions%E2%80%99%20struggle%20to%20hold%20platforms%20accountable%20continues%2C%20the%20platforms%20themselves%20are%20also%20pushing%20for%20new%20forms%20of%20alternatives%20to%20unions%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faapti.in%2Fblog%2Fbuilding-the-driver-advisory-council%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edriver%20advisory%20councils%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20unions%20gain%20prominence%20and%20political%20parties%20show%20willingness%20to%20address%20platform%20workers%E2%80%99%20concerns%2C%20the%20era%20of%20unregulated%20platforms%20appears%20to%20be%20ending.%20The%20upcoming%20Telangana%20elections%20could%20also%20decide%20whether%20a%20change%20in%20the%20government%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20welfare%20law%20for%20workers.%20The%20platform%20workers%20are%20optimistic%20and%20have%20clearly%20said%20that%20their%20vote%20will%20go%20to%20the%20political%20parties%20that%20would%20address%20their%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20commercial%20driver%20from%20the%20union%20expressed%20his%20displeasure%20with%20the%20current%20development%20model%20of%20Telangana%20which%20is%20ignoring%20them%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20development%20of%20Telangana%20is%20different%20from%20the%20development%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana.%20The%20development%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20need%20not%20mean%20they%20are%20happy%2C%20we%20are%20not%20happy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699941941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F12090306%2F22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fahead-of-telangana-elections-gig-workers-union-demands-a-rajasthan-like-welfare-law%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20unions%20gain%20prominence%20and%20political%20parties%20show%20willingness%20to%20address%20platform%20workers'%20concerns%2C%20the%20era%20of%20unregulated%20platforms%20appears%20to%20be%20ending.%20The%20upcoming%20Telangana%20elections%20could%20also%20decide%20the%20course%20of%20a%20welfare%20law%20for%20workers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fahead-of-telangana-elections-gig-workers-union-demands-a-rajasthan-like-welfare-law%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Ira%20Khan%20as%20a%20Marathi%20to%20be%20bride%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699941933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105201397%2Cimgsize-33556.cms%22%2C%22originID%2