of%20summiting%20Blackhead%20Peak%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%2F%3Ffbid%3D730359155783310%26set%3Dpcb.730359192449973%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETaos%20Search%20and%20Rescue%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Remarkably%2C%20the%20dog%20was%20found%20alive%20and%20beside%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20information%20from%20the%20Archuleta%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20The%20Denver%20Gazette%2C%20Moore%20and%20his%20dog%20disappeared%20when%20they%20had%20intended%20to%20reach%20the%20summit%20of%20Blackhead%20Peak%2C%20situated%20approximately%2020%20miles%20to%20the%20east%20of%20Pagosa%20Springs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Moore's%20remains%20were%20discovered%20on%20October%2030%20in%20the%20Lower%20Blanco%20drainage%20basin%20by%20a%20hunter.%20This%20valley%20is%20situated%20southeast%20of%20the%20summit%20of%20Blackhead%20Peak.%20The%20sheriff's%20office%20stated%20that%20Moore's%20white%20Jack%20Russell%20terrier%2C%20Finney%2C%20was%20found%20beside%20his%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2031%2C%20members%20of%20the%20sheriff's%20office%20and%20a%20search%20and%20rescue%20team%20were%20airlifted%20into%20the%20area%20to%20locate%20and%20retrieve%20Moore's%20body%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Gazette%20and%20the%20sheriff's%20office.%20Finney%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20veterinary%20hospital%20for%20treatment%20and%20has%20since%20been%20joyfully%20reunited%20with%20her%20family%2C%20officials%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20cause%20of%20Moore's%20death%20but%20assured%20that%20foul%20play%20is%20not%20suspected%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fcolorado-hiker-missing-since-august-dead-dog-found-alive-next-body%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECBS%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESituated%20in%20the%20southwestern%20region%20of%20Colorado%2C%20the%20San%20Juan%20Mountains%2C%20Blackhead%20Peak%20boasts%20an%