rlfriend%2057%20times%20after%20an%20argument%20over%20breadcrumbs%20has%20been%20released%20from%20jail%20due%20to%20a%20court%20ruling%20that%20the%20high-calorie%20diet%20served%20in%20the%20facility%20could%20kill%20him.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dimitri%20Fricano%20viciously%20killed%20his%2025-year-old%20girlfriend%20Erika%20Preti%20while%20the%20pair%20were%20vacationing%20in%20Sardinia%20in%202017.%20He%20weighed%20around%20120%20kilograms%20when%20he%20was%20jailed%20for%2030%20years%20in%202019%2C%20however%2C%20because%20of%20delays%20caused%20by%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20he%20did%20not%20begin%20serving%20his%20sentence%20until%20April%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20Turin%20Surveillance%20Court%20in%20Italy%20has%20freed%20Mr%20Fricano%20on%20medical%20grounds%20after%20just%20a%20year%20behind%20bars.%20As%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F11%2F13%2Fnews%2F440-pound-convicted-killer-spared-prison-over-bad-diet%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20prison%20officials%20said%20that%20the%2035-year-old's%20health%20is%20at%20risk%20because%20they%20cannot%20provide%20the%20low-calorie%20diet%20he%20needs%20to%20slim%20down.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20Mr%20Fricano's%20weight%20had%20ballooned%20up%20to%20200kgs%20in%20just%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20court%20ruled%20that%20Mr%20Fricano%20can%20no%20longer%20remain%20behind%20bars%20because%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bincompatible%20with%20the%20prison%20regime%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20his%20heft%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20him%20to%20get%20around%20without%20a%20wheelchair%20or%20crutches.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20chain%20smoker%2C%20the%20court%20noted.%20Further%2C%20the%20judges%20in%20Italy%20stated%20that%20the%2035-year-old's%20incarceration%20also%20puts%20his%20life%20at%20risk%20because%20prison%20officials%20are%20unable%20to%20provide%20the%20l