eels%20like%20it%E2%80%99s%20droning%20on.%20Ten%20months%20ago%2C%20Salman%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Tiger%20showed%20up%20to%20rescue%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Pathaan%20in%20the%20Siddharth%20Anand%20film%2C%20his%20checkered%20scarf%20getting%20some%20of%20the%20loudest%20cheers%20in%20the%20theatre.%20In%20Maneesh%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ETiger%203%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20returns%20the%20favour%2C%20by%20announcing%20his%20character%E2%80%99s%20arrival%20more%20literally%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Jhoome%20Jo%20Pathaan%E2%80%99%2C%20composed%20by%20Vishal-Shekhar%2C%20plays%20in%20a%20portable%20speaker%20and%20explodes%20seconds%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Cem%3EPathaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20there%20was%20a%20playfulness%20to%20the%20Khans%20teaming%20up%20to%20do%20action%20together%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20%3Cem%3EKaran%20Arjun%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1995)%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20winky%20banter%20about%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20the%20nation%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20leave%20it%20to%20the%20young%20ones.%20In%20Tiger%203%20however%2C%20the%20banter%20feels%20jaded%2C%20the%20action%20set-pieces%20seem%20to%20lack%20purpose%20and%20what%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20joyous%20reunion%2C%20begins%20to%20feel%20like%20an%20obligation%20towards%20the%20cinematic%20universe%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98spyverse%E2%80%99%20as%20producers%20YRF%20calls%20this%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20in%20the%20care%20and%20affection%20to%20set%20these%20sequences%20up%20in%20the%20respective%20films%2C%20also%20ends%20up%20being%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20films.%20While%20Anand%E2%80%99s%20film%20felt%20like%20it%20had%20light%20feet%20and%20coasted%20on%20charm%2C%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20film%20feels%20stodgy%2C%20bearing%20the%20weight%20of%20a%20star%2C%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20wish%20to%20take%20even%20the%20smallest%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FvEjTUDjjU6A%3Fsi%3DE0_9Zl2iUkzYQ9ZL%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20Maneesh%20Sharma%20has%20never%20imposed%20a%20signature%20on%20his%20films.%20While%20that%20can%20often%20be%20an%20asset%20for%20a%20franchise%20film%2C%20a%20director%E2%80%99s%20less-than-distinct%20vision%20is%20also%20revealed%20fairly%20quickly.%20Like%20it%20often%20does%20for%20spies%2C%20the%20past%20comes%20back%20for%20Zoya%20and%20Tiger.%20A%20disenchanted%20patriot%20(Emraan%20Hashmi)%2C%20comes%20for%20the%20two%20super%20spies%20and%20their%20son%2C%20unimaginatively%20called%20Junior.%20What%20follows%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20renegade%20missions%2C%20the%20spectacular%20line%20around%20the%20interval%20point%20%E2%80%9CZoya%20%3Cem%3Ebhabhi%20ne%20%3C%2Fem%3ETiger%3Cem%3E%20bhai%20ko%20dhokha%20de%20diya%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20(Did%20Zoya%20bhabhi%20betray%20Tiger%20bhai%3F)%20and%20a%20maniac%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98vision%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20future%20of%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20we%E2%80%99re%20watching%20an%20extravagant%20spy%20film%2C%20Tiger%203%E2%80%99s%20opening%20scenes%20feel%20grounded%20and%20promising.%20A%20large%20part%20of%20it%20is%20because%20of%20Sridhar%20Raghavan%E2%80%99s%20fluent%20dialogue%20and%20Hashmi%E2%80%99s%20unsettling%20presence.%20Playing%20the%20part%20of%20a%20disgraced%20ISI%20agent%20Aatish%20Rehman%20%E2%80%93%20who%20worked%20with%20Zoya%E2%80%99s%20(Kaif%E2%80%99s)%20father%20%E2%80%93%20Hashmi%20feels%20relaxed%2C%20and%20yet%20focused.%20He%E2%80%99s%20never%20been%20regarded%20as%20the%20most%20promising%20talent%20around%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20nice%20to%20witness%20his%20growth%20over%20the%20years.%20One%20can%20sense%20a%20hunger%20in%20him%20to%20improve%20as%20an%20actor%2C%20which%20becomes%20all%20the%20more%20apparent%20when%20he%E2%80%99s%20pitted%20against%20the%20leading%20man%20in%20Tiger%203-it%20is%20he%20who%20makes%20that%20extra%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fine%20villain%20apart%2C%20Tiger%203%20falters%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20very%20little%20in%20terms%20of%20personality%20to%20the%20titular%20spy.%20No%20one%20walked%20into%20Maneesh%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20film%20thinking%20Salman%20Khan%20would%20deliver%20something%20in%20the%20same%20vein%20as%20Tom%20Cruise%20or%20Keanu%20Reeves%2C%20but%20the%20audience%20deserves%20to%20see%20at%20least%20some%20effort%2C%20does%20it%20not%3F%20Khan%20goes%20through%20the%20motions%2C%20without%20breaking%20a%20sweat%2C%20and%20a%20furrowed-brow%20expression.%20There%E2%80%99s%20simply%20no%20human%20characteristic%20to%20the%20spy%2C%20other%20than%20his%20physicality%20and%20boring%2C%20ugly%20swagger.%20How%20much%20of%20a%20film%20can%20be%20shouldered%20on%20a%20star%E2%80%99s%20swagger%20alone%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14111019%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.09.2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14111019%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.09.2.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14111019%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.09.2-300x127.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14111019%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.09.2-1024x432.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684616%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22506%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Tiger%203%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Katrina%20Kaif%E2%80%99s%20Zoya%20keeps%20getting%20the%20shorter%20end%20of%20the%20stick.%20Kaif%20is%20a%20much%20more%20dynamic%20action%20star%20than%20Khan%20%E2%80%93%20something%20she%20showcases%20in%20a%20fight%20sequence%20that%20takes%20place%20in%20a%20Hammam%20bath.%20However%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20relegated%20as%20a%20device%20to%20explain%20to%20the%20audience%20everything%20that%20the%20characters%20are%20doing%20%E2%80%93%20so%20that%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20on%20board.%20The%20result%20is%20she%20is%20offered%20little%20in%20terms%20of%20personality%2C%20lest%20she%20outshine%20the%20hero.%20Revathy%2C%20who%20replaces%20the%20late%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fgirish-karnad-homage%5C%22%3EGirish%20Karnad%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20R%26amp%3BAW%20chief%20in%20the%20film%2C%20keeps%20the%20repartee%20snappy%20with%20her%20agents.%20In%20one%20scene%2C%20she%20tells%20a%20few%20of%20them%20how%20Yerwada%20jail%20only%20offers%20one%20soap%20to%20its%20inmates%20to%20bathe%20and%20wash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20films%20in%20YRF%E2%80%99s%20spy%20universe%2C%20even%20Tiger%203%20keeps%20up%20the%20pretence%20of%20championing%20secular%20values.%20The%20distinction%20between%20the%20radical%20Pakistani%20army%20and%20peace-loving%20Pakistanis%20is%20made%20more%20than%20once.%20Tiger%20keeps%20referring%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20as%20his%20%3Cem%3Emaayka%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20married%20woman%E2%80%99s%20mother%E2%80%99s%20home)%20%E2%80%93%20an%20endearing%20touch.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20moment%20really%20arrives%2C%20Tiger%203%20isn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20hide%20its%20intent%20to%20ride%20the%20wave%20of%20hideous%20jingoism.%20It%20becomes%20visible%20in%20a%20choice%20%E2%80%93%20when%20an%20ISI%20agent%20is%20shot%20dead%2C%20but%20the%20R%26amp%3BAW%20spy%E2%80%99s%20throat%20is%20sliced%20open.%20The%20good-natured%2C%20peace-loving%20Pakistani%20prime%20minister%20(Simran)%20kicks%20off%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20independence%20day%20celebrations%20with%20the%20Indian%20national%20anthem.%20Even%20for%20a%20Salman%20Khan%20film%2C%20and%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20times%20when%20patriotic%20fantasies%20seem%20to%20know%20no%20bounds%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20stretch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Pathaan%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20paraphrases%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20in%20the%20climax%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20soldier%20asks%20what%20they%20can%20do%20for%20their%20country%2C%20not%20what%20a%20country%20can%20do%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%20In%20Salman%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%20where%20the%20stakes%20for%20million%20dollar%20set-pieces%20feel%20inconsequential%2C%20the%20emotional%20beats%20feel%20insincere%20and%20the%20patriotism%20almost%20begins%20to%20seem%20like%20a%20surrogate%20to%20the%20country%20asking%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20more%20can%20we%20do%20to%20further%20Salman%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20swagger%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20of%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20156%20minutes%20are%20comatose%20though.%20Salman%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Tiger%20has%20one%20moment%20of%20grace.%20Hurtling%20down%20using%20a%20parachute%20with%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Pathaan%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20reminded%20how%20the%20two%20super%20spies%20have%20just%20the%20one%20parachute%20between%20them.%20Tiger%20offers%20it%20to%20Pathaan%20saying%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EWaise%20bhi%20tere%20udte%20huye%20baal%20aur%20bhi%20achhe%20lagte%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Your%20flying%20hair%20makes%20you%20look%20cooler).%E2%80%9D%20Generosity%2C%20now%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20human%20characteristic%20that%20Tiger%20could%E2%80%99ve%20used%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699940806000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14110940%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.09.06%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Ftiger-3-salman-khan-shahrukh-katrina-kaif%22%2C%22summ