%20alt%3D%5C%22michael%20flynn%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58a34c106e09a835008b6e8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELori%20and%20Valerie%20Flynn%2C%20Michael%20Flynn's%20wife%20and%20sister-in-law%2C%20are%20suing%20CNN%20for%20defamation.%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMichael%20Flynn's%20family%20kept%20money%20donated%20to%20his%20legal%20fund%2C%20according%20to%20new%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFilings%20from%20CNN%20revealed%20testimony%20by%20Flynn's%20sister%2C%C2%A0Barbara%20Flynn%20Redgate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFlynn's%20wife%2C%20Lori%2C%20and%20sister-in-law%2C%20Valerie%2C%20are%20suing%20CNN%20and%20accusing%20the%20network%20of%20defamation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERetired%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELt.%20Gen.%20Michael%20Flynn's%20family%20fundraised%20for%20his%20legal%20defense%20fund%20from%20QAnon%20supporters%20and%20then%20kept%20the%20extra%20money%20once%20his%20lawyers%20were%20paid%20off%2C%20according%20to%20new%20court%20filings%20unsealed%20in%20a%20defamation%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20documents%20%E2%80%94%20filed%20by%20CNN%20as%20part%20of%20a%20defamation%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20Flynn's%20wife%2C%20Lori%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichael-flynn-sister-in-law-sues-cnn-linking-her-qanon-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esister-in-law%2C%20Valerie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20against%20the%20network%20%E2%80%94%20cite%20deposition%20by%20Flynn's%20sister%2C%20Barbara%20Flynn%20Redgate%2C%20who%20was%20a%20trustee%20of%20Flynn's%20legal%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semafor.com%2Farticle%2F11%2F13%2F2023%2Fmichael-flynn-and-family-pocketed-leftover-money-from-legal-defense-fund-filing-claims%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESemafor%20first%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20unsealed%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELori%20and%20Valerie%20Flynn%20allege%20that%20in%202021%20CNN%20defamed%20them%20by%20airing%20a%20clip%20it%20said%20was%20of%20Flynn%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etaking%20an%20%26quot%3Boath%26quot%3B%20connected%20to%20the%20QAnon%20conspiracy%20theory%20while%20his%20family%20members%20stand%20beside%20him%20with%20their%20right%20hands%20raised.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unsealed%20court%20documents%20were%20part%20of%20CNN's%20attempt%20to%20have%20the%20defamation%20case%20tossed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlynn%20Redgate%2C%20who%20oversaw%20donations%20to%20Flynn's%20legal%20fund%2C%20agreed%20in%20testimony%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20mind%20taking%20money%20from%20people%20who%20%5Bused%20QAnon%5D%20hashtags%26quot%3B%20as%20long%20as%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bdirecting%20%5Bpeople%5D%20to%20the%20legal%20defense%20fund%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20documents%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBarbara%20testified%20that%2C%20once%20legal%20fees%20were%20paid%2C%20the%20Flynns%20themselves%20received%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20from%20CNN%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlynn%20is%20a%20retired%20US%20Army%20lieutenant%20general%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20ally%20who%20briefly%20served%20as%20the%20president's%20national%20security%20adviser%20and%20later%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20lying%20to%20the%20FBI%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retired%20general%20and%20his%20family%20began%20garnering%20donations%20in%202017%20while%20Flynn%20was%20facing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-trump-pay-legal-fees-for-michael-flynn-russia-investigation-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20investigation%20over%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Flynn%20family%20ultimately%20pocketed%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20from%20the%20fund%2C%20according%20to%20Semafor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJared%20Roberts%2C%20an%20attorney%20representing%20the%20Flynn%20family%20members%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20comment%20to%20Semafor%2C%20Roberts%20said%20CNN%20has%20%26quot%3Bresorted%20to%20inappropriate%20mischaracterization%20of%20deposition%20testimony%20and%20the%20facts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20intend%20to%20fight%20this%20case%20in%20the%20media%20and%20we%20will%20make%20our%20response%20according%20to%20the%20scheduling%20order%20of%20the%20court%20and%20in%20our%20opposition%20brief%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20CNN%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CNN%20report%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20suit%20primarily%20focused%20on%20a%20QAnon%20conference%2C%20but%20also%20featured%20the%20aforementioned%20clip%20of%20the%20apparent%20%26quot%3Boath.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlynn's%20brother%20and%20another%20sister-in-law%20are%20also%20suing%20CNN%20in%20a%20separate%20case%20still%20pending%20in%20New%20York%20federal%20court%2C%20according%20to%20Semafor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20court%20filings%2C%20CNN%20alleges%20that%20Flynn%20and%20his%20family%20leaned%20into%20the%20conspiracy%20theorist%20community%20and%20used%20them%20for%20fundraising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20QAnon%20post%20in%20June%202020%20shared%20the%20oath%2C%20the%20network%20noted%20in%20the%20filing%2C%20that%20Michael%20Flynn%20changed%20his%20Twitter%20profile%20to%20include%20the%20hashtag%20%26quot%3BTakeTheOath.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recording%20of%20a%20phone%20call%20between%20Flynn%20and%20GOP%20lawyer%20Lin%20Wood%20released%20in%202021%2C%20Flynn%20said%20he%20believed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflynn-said-he-thinks-qanon-is-disinformation-total-nonsense-2021-11%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQAnon%20is%20%26quot%3Bto