e2cff94bee11be6f00224828d4ab-c3a4581293db4542b34d10e1524fe78f%26esid%3Db1cdf4b6-3f82-ee11-8179-00224828d4ab%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20Affiliates'%20Chief%20Investment%20Officer%20Jim%20Masturzo%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-looks-like-1987-no-october-crash-2023-10%5C%22%3Ecorrective%20slump%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20hit%20markets%20in%20October%20was%20a%20potential%20sign%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20transitioning%20away%20from%20post-pandemic%20distortions%2C%20such%20as%20high%20savings%20that%20have%20largely%20been%20consumed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20the%20current%20selloff%20as%20a%20potential%20inflection%20point%20in%20the%20transition%20from%20a%20decade%20of%20abundance%20to%20one%20of%20austerity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20will%20ignite%20pain%20for%20equity%20and%20long-term%20fixed%20income%20markets%2C%20as%20prices%20respond%20to%20an%20increasing%20cohort%20of%20risk-off%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20marks%20a%20major%20shift%20in%20the%20investing%20environment.%20Before%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20sharply%20increased%20rates%20to%20a%205.25%25-5.50%25%20over%20the%20last%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20markets%20enjoyed%20an%20era%20of%20ultra-low%20interest%20rates%20that%20followed%20the%202008%20financial%20crash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20no%20one%20stopped%20the%20music%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20this%20game%20of%20macroeconomic%20musical%20chairs%20cannot%20go%20on%20forever%2C%26quot%3B%20Masturzo%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20tighter%20monetary%20policy%20in%20a%20period%20of%20high%20deficit%20spending%20mean%20US%20Treasury%20yields%20will%20continue%20climbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHigher%20rates%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20lower%20asset%20prices%2C%20unleashing%20a%20vicious%2